# macOS
.DS_Store
# Xcode
build/
DerivedData/
*.xcuserstate
**/xcuserdata/
# Rust
target/
# local agent settings (never commit; may hold machine-local config)
.claude/
# internal worklog — never shipped (R5: no personal infra in tracked files)
STATUS.md

# APNs auth keys — never commit (belt-and-suspenders; keys live outside the tree)
*.p8

# cruft
_removed-python/
*.fuse_hidden*

# Local personalization overlay — never commit (holds the owner's real name,
# languages, vocabulary). Ship jesse.example.toml; copy it to jesse.local.toml
# and edit that. See README → "Make Jesse yours".
jesse.local.toml

# Local CI-guard denylist — the owner's real name/hostnames/IPs the R5 guard
# should catch locally. Ship scripts/ci-guards.local.sh.example; copy it. Org CI
# won't have this file, which is expected.
scripts/ci-guards.local.sh

# Local eval suites pinned to a real vault (real facts, filenames). The shipped
# vaultqa-example.json is the generic template; real suites live here, gitignored.
eval/suites/local/
